---
title: Bacon & Veggie Fried Rice with Greens & Chilli Flakes
description: Get dinner on the table in a flash with this shortcut superstar! Tonight’s fried rice is loaded with crispy bacon, colourful veggies, Asian greens and a kick of chilli flakes - all stir-fried to sizzling perfection.

*We’ve replaced the baby broccoli in this recipe with broccoli due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
